# Windsurf Rules for Lumina Knowledge Engine

> Project: Lumina Knowledge Engine - A modern RAG system for semantic document search
> Architecture: Go (Crawler) + Python/FastAPI (Brain) + Next.js 15 (Portal) + Qdrant (Vector DB)

---

## 🎯 Project Overview

**Current Status (MVP Complete)**:
- ✅ Go Crawler fetches HTML and sends JSON to Python
- ✅ Python Brain API embeds content and stores in Qdrant
- ✅ Next.js 15 Portal connects to Python for semantic search
- ✅ Dark/Light mode via next-themes (Tailwind v4)

**Known Issues**:
1. Theme toggle button not triggering dark mode correctly (check `globals.css` @theme config)
2. Go crawler grabs raw HTML warnings; needs better content extraction

**Next Goals**:
1. Text chunking in Python before embedding
2. LLM integration (DeepSeek/OpenAI) for summary answers
3. PDF/Markdown file ingestion support

